<BODY LANG="en-US" DIR="LTR">
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><I>Description:</I></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">An employee requests for vacation. The
boss accepts or declines the request. If request was rejected, the
employee receives notification and business process ends. If request
was approved,  the human resource inspectors receive task &ldquo;check
rules and technologies&rdquo;. Human resource inspector checks
business process data. If check result is negative, the business
process returns to the &ldquo;evaluate a request&rdquo; state (the
cycle example). Boss accepts or declines the request. If the check
result is positive, the business process sends task for hardcopy
request submission and official order issuing. Employee receives task
&ldquo;submit the written request for a vacation&rdquo; to the human
resource department&rdquo;, the human resource inspector receives
task &ldquo;receive a written request from employee&rdquo;
concurrently. Upon completion this task the human resource inspector
receives next task &ldquo;make an official order&rdquo;. After all
these tasks are done, the business process ends.</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><I>Note</I>. Organization function
determines boss for every actor. Actors with login names starting
with &ldquo;g&rdquo; have boss <I>julius</I>, the others &ndash;
<I>nero</I>.</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><I>How to play the business process:</I></P>
<OL>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Log in as member of <I>staff</I>
	group (e.g. <I>marcus</I>)</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Click on the menu item &ldquo;Process
	Definitions&rdquo;</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Click &ldquo;Start&rdquo; for 
	&ldquo;vacation demo&rdquo;</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Start form will appeared. In this
	form: 
	</P>
</OL>
<UL>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Enter the time interval for the
	vacation</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Fill the fields  &laquo;reason&raquo;
	and &laquo;comment&raquo;</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</P>
</UL>
<P STYLE="margin-left: 0.98in; margin-bottom: 0in">The new instance
of &ldquo;vacation demo&rdquo; business process will start and boss
receives the &ldquo;evaluate a request&rdquo; task. The boss of
<I>marcus</I> is <I>nero</I></P>
<OL START=5>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click
	&ldquo;Logout&rdquo; </FONT>
	</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Login as
	<I>nero</I></FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click on
	&ldquo;evaluate a request&rdquo; task</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Choose
	&ldquo;accept&rdquo;, fill the &laquo;boss comment&raquo; and click
	&laquo;OK&raquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click
	&ldquo;Logout&rdquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Login as
	member of the &ldquo;human resource&rdquo; group. (<I>cleopatra</I>)</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click
	&ldquo;check rules and technologies&rdquo; task</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Choose
	&ldquo;correct&rdquo;, fill the &ldquo;human resource inspector
	comment&rdquo; and click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click on
	&ldquo;Receive a written request&rdquo; task</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Login as
	<I>marcus</I>. Click on &ldquo;Submit a written request&rdquo; task
	and then click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Login as
	<I>cleopatra</I>. Click on &ldquo;Make an official order&rdquo;
	task. </FONT>
	</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>The form
	will appeared. In this form: </FONT>
	</P>
</OL>
<UL>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Fill the &ldquo;Official
	order number&rdquo; field</FONT></P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Fill the &ldquo;Official
	order date&rdquo; field</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><FONT SIZE=3>Click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</FONT></P>
</UL>
<P STYLE="margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in">The business
process ends</P>
